From 174ca907cba74a7fed73dd9aab34929cfafc5f90 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "SengKai,Tan" <seng.kai.tan@intel.com>
Date: Wed, 18 May 2016 16:54:23 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2163/2508] ALSA: hda - Increase default bdl_pos_adj for
 Broxton-P

commit c1791105168d006a039bb558df18a3d875dbb8b7 from
https://github.com/01org/linux-apollolake-i

Similar to other Atom processors, set Broxton-P bdl_pos_adj
value to 32.

Signed-off-by: Tan, Seng Kai <seng.kai.tan@intel.com>
---
 sound/pci/hda/hda_intel.c |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/sound/pci/hda/hda_intel.c b/sound/pci/hda/hda_intel.c
index 0ff5465..c5f176f 100644
--- a/sound/pci/hda/hda_intel.c
+++ b/sound/pci/hda/hda_intel.c
@@ -1513,6 +1513,7 @@ static int default_bdl_pos_adj(struct azx *chip)
 		switch (chip->pci->device) {
 		case 0x0f04: /* Baytrail */
 		case 0x2284: /* Braswell */
+		case 0x5a98: /* Broxton-P */
 			return 32;
 		}
 	}
